#

Jalapeño Popper Burger

30 min
$12.99
650 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

DairyGluten

Dietary Tags:

High ProteinLow Carb

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Main

Tags:

BurgerSpicyComfort Food

Description

A spicy twist on the classic burger, topped with creamy cheese and zesty jalapeños for an unforgettable flavor.

Ingredients

  • ground beef: 1 lb
  • cream cheese: 4 oz
  • shredded cheddar cheese: 1/2 cup
  • jalapeños: 2, diced
  • burger buns: 4
  • lettuce: 4 leaves
  • tomato: 1, sliced
  • pickles: 4 slices
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • garlic powder: 1 tsp
  • onion powder: 1 tsp
